Uttar Pradesh
Sep 09, 2014
Street Harassment
Description:
			A youth has been arrested in a village here for allegedly teasing a girl.

Sandeep Kumar allegedly teased the girl in Almaspur village last evening.

Seeing this, locals nabbed him, beat him up and then handed him over to police.

The parents of the girl, who works with private company, have alleged that Sandeep teased her while she was on her way to office, they added.

